author: Danny Schwartz
title: Future "Draco" Video
text:
Posted by Danny Schwartz , Feb 22, 2017 at 10:23am Subscribe to HNHH TV Future shares the video for "Draco," the first single from his self-titled album. 
Hours after performing "Draco" on The Tonight Show With Jimmy Fallon , Future has released the song's music video. 
Future will release HNDRXX , his second album in two weeks, this Friday. Future shares the video for "Draco," the first single from his self-titled album.
